@node "Requirements" "Requirements          "
@next "InstallUse"
@{b}@{u}What do you need to use Clock?@{ub}@{uu}

 * Amiga with Kickstart 2.x or 3.x

 (This programm is not tested on Kickstart 2.x if you find some
  error send E-mail to Author)

@endnode

@node "InstallUse" "Installation and Usage"
@next "Distribution"
@prev "Requirements"
@{b}Here's how you install Clock onto your system:@{ub}

 @{b}1)@{ub} Copy Clock in some directory.

 @{b}2)@{ub} Start Clock in Startup-sequence like this:

    (ClockDir):ClockV1.3

    or click twise on Clock icon.

@endnode

